Package vooga.towerdefense.gameeditor.gamemaker.editorscreens

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FinishScreen
    FinishScreen helps the game developer save the game he/she has been editing to a file.
    GameEditorScreen
    Super class that makes common behavior for each of the editor screens.
    GameElementEditorScreen
    GameElementEditorScreen is responsible for helping the game developer make game elements.
    LevelEditorScreen
    LevelEditorScreen is responsible for helping the game developer make levels.
    PlayerEditorScreen
    PlayerEditorScreen helps the game developer edit default attributes for the player.
    RuleEditorScreen
    RuleEditorScreen is responsible for helping the game developer add rules to their game.
    StartUpScreen
    StartUpScreen starts the GameEditor for the game developer.
    ViewEditorScreen
    ViewEditorScreen is responsible for helping the game developer make the view.
